OL,5, Caroline Flack's mother has criticised 
OL,6, ITV over its handling of ex-This       
OL,7, Morning host Phillip Schofield and says
OL,8, the broadcaster has failed to learn    
OL,9, from the death of her daughter.        
OL,11,FPresenters are not always protected,   
OL,12,FChristine Flack told BBC Newsnight.    
OL,14,FIn a BBC interview, Schofield          
OL,15,Fapologised for lying about his affair  
OL,16,Fand said he had "lost everything".     
OL,18,FITV says it feels "badly let down" by  
OL,19,FSchofield and has insisted it takes its
OL,20,F"duty of care seriously".              
